item.title: CVE-2018-5234|2024-08-05T05:33:43.639Z -- symantec%20corporation -- norton%20core
item.description: The Norton Core router prior to v237 may be susceptible to a command injection exploit. This is a type of attack in which the goal is execution of arbitrary commands on the host system via vulnerable software.
